/06\/mercy-believers-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":7655,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Curses: O Allah, have mercy on believers I cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I am only a human being. Whenever I scold, curse, or punish a Muslim man, then turn it into purification and mercy for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6361, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2601 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25470,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/29\/using-vessels-kuffar-mushrikin\/","url_meta":{"origin":7655,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Utensils: Using the dishware of idolaters if necessary","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Imran ibn Hussein reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and his companions performed ablution from the waterskin of an idolatrous woman. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 337, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 682 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064f\u0635\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u0644\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0